{"tid":170212,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"研究顯示 1日1杯啤酒 有效預防心臟病","createTime":"2017-03-24T15:06:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-28T22:44:49.000Z","uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3ce3792a4ebaedc2d1aec7eb41e1ccc360a77536","tid":170212,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T15:06:22.000Z","msg":"轉貼：<br />\n<a href=\"http://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/1726538/日飲1杯啤酒%20減患心臟病風險\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fskypost.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F1726538%2F%E6%97%A5%E9%A3%B21%E6%9D%AF%E5%95%A4%E9%85%92%2520%E6%B8%9B%E6%82%A3%E5%BF%83%E8%87%9F%E7%97%85%E9%A2%A8%E9%9A%AA&d=NEeHCsu%2FqEZuPycg%2B0xSpviMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=2fd9d5fe\" target=\"_blank\">http://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/1726538/日飲1杯啤酒%20減患心臟病風險</a><br />\n<br />\n日飲1杯啤酒 減患心臟病風險<br />\n2017/03/24  <br />\n<br />\n研究員指，適量飲酒的人較大量飲酒，甚至從來不喝酒的人，患心臟疾病的會較細。研究結果已刊登在《英國醫學期刊》。（路透社資料圖片）<br />\n<br />\n英國《獨立報》引述一項研究指出，在查閱近200萬名英國健康成年人的電子健康記錄之後，發現一名正常成年人，每周喝不超過14個單位的酒精，即是每天1杯約500毫升的啤酒，有機會減少患上心絞痛、心臟衰竭，以及因心臟血管瘤引致中風等7種心臟疾病。<br />\n<br />\n研究員指，適量飲酒的人較大量飲酒，甚至從來不喝酒的人，患心臟疾病的會較細。研究結果已刊登在《英國醫學期刊》。<br />\n<br />\n劍橋大學學者與其他大學研究員分析指，適量飲酒的人較少機會患上各種炎症，亦攝取到對身體較好的膽固醇，相對減少患上某些心臟疾病，但不代表鼓勵人喝酒，多做運動及均衡飲食才是預防心臟病良方。"},{"pid":"3e2d6e5cbf573269ba109c773761dc4c11729700","tid":170212,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T15:15:48.000Z","msg":"幾多年後又推翻呢個研究"},{"pid":"1dd054f6d9a6ba0bc3f667b446a9f62cb17c7895","tid":170212,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T16:48:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾多年後又推翻呢個研究</blockquote><br />\n可能真係預防心臟病嘅<br />\n不過對個肝有咩影響就唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"459a5e2cd7140815e9a77040deac1bbab0e9058d","tid":170212,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T15:19:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5306c16b0166999f35bfc5098b9b3913268878d0","tid":170212,"uid":21514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T16:10:02.000Z","msg":"我係一日一罐<br />\n但係肥左好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b2dda8d7393504af46aeceecbd9b711dfe543ce","tid":170212,"uid":36964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T16:15:34.000Z","msg":"BMJ喎<br />\n不過飲完個啤酒肚點搞先?"},{"pid":"6af527412be4712e9e635431aac444519e8a9b6f","tid":170212,"uid":78443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T16:18:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>BMJ喎<br />\n不過飲完個啤酒肚點搞先?</blockquote><br />\n增加患痴肥風險"},{"pid":"98d9f31270d1985b8f2c66a40b86901ce6c0e354","tid":170212,"uid":41908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T17:32:59.000Z","msg":"英國研究<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b8cd1a95ee58830df846b90c3f62b50e5f71bd5","tid":170212,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T22:44:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>英國研究<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n劍橋大學喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}